<author>ạ̉ymn kfrwny, ạ̉ymn kfrwny</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - ạ̹nt srwry wsẖbʿy ạ̹nt wfrḥẗ ʿmry fyk
 wḥdk mạlk qlby ạ̹nt wḥdk mạ fy sẖryk
 jwạty fy sẖwq kbyr ạ̹nk nfsy wnbḍy tṣyr
 wmạtmrq mn ʿmry lḥẓẗ ạ̹lạã wfyhạ ạ̹nt
 1- sẖw ṭʿmthạ ạ̉yạmy lw sẖltk mn qdạmy
 ṣạḥy wlạ bmnạmy lw sẖltk mn qdạmy
 ʿmltlk byn ḍlwʿy ʿrsẖ mnḍf bdmwʿy
 wḥty̱ tmlk yạ yswʿy btstạhl ʿrsẖy ạ̹hdyk
 2- rby sẖkry wtsbyḥy wṣwty wlḥny wmdyḥy
 bqlby wlḥmy yạ msyḥy bhtf bạsmk wbʿlyk
 bjwʿy ạ̹nt btkfyny bʿṭsẖy ạ̹nt btrwyny
 wbʿd ạlmwt btḥyyny wạlạ̉bdyẗ bʿysẖhạ fyk</lyrics>
<title>ạ̹nt srwry</title>
</song>